name: The Collective "Unbroken" Wristband
description:
Join the movement with The Collective "Unbroken" Wristband! Wristbands on outside say "TheAlohaCollective.com" and "Aloha Where You're @" w/ "UNBROKEN" embossed on the inside.

Wristbands come in five (5) color options: Black w/ Gold lettering; Gold w/ Black lettering; Black w/ White lettering; Charged Green w/ Black lettering; and Pink w/ White lettering.

Portion of proceeds will benefit the Hawaii Foodbank and Family Programs Hawaii, working to keep keiki and their families UNBROKEN!

name: The Collective "Unbroken" Trucker (All Black)
description:
The Collective is bringing sexy back to the trucker.  Each of our signature truckers was built to keep our Keiki (children) "Unbroken" through Family Programs Hawaii (FPH).  FPH's objective is to provide services to prevent children from entering foster care; support children and families involved in the foster care system; and assist youth transitioning out of care. Spread ALOHA and keep our children UNBROKEN where you're @ with the Collective Truckers.
